PARRY: Manually parry an incoming attack

Syntax: parry

DESCRIPTION:
  Attempts to parry the next incoming melee attack in combat. Each parry
  attempt costs 1 APM. You must have a weapon or shield wielded to parry.

  Parry bonus: +1 per PP above 10 (Physical Prowess attribute).

  For automatic parrying every round, use: autoparry on

SEE ALSO: autoparry, dodge, autododge, combat
